    "400420": {
        "Desc": "Collect materials used to make Magic Pockets",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Whaaaat?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}? Paimon?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Charlotte!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's Charlotte!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "I never guessed I'd bump into you while riding the aquabus. In the story of my life, this is big news!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "What are you doing in Fontaine? I didn't hear anything about you paying us a visit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, it's quite the coincidence! But as Travelers, we're always on the move. It's not surprising that nobody knew we were coming."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, though we still have no idea how the Hydro Archon knew about us... Oh! Let Paimon introduce you to our new friends!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Oh, no need for introductions, Paimon. I would recognize the Great Magician Lyney and his assistant Lynette anywhere."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "I wouldn't be much of a reporter if I didn't know who they were. It's a pleasure to meet you! I'm Charlotte, a reporter for The Steambird."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Nice to meet you. From The Steambird, huh? We've often relied on your paper to promote our performances."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "It's an honor to meet you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, now that everyone knows each other, Fontaine suddenly doesn't feel like such an unfamiliar place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, what have you been up to lately, Charlotte? Any big news?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Not too much... when there isn't any breaking news, I mainly cover the trials at the opera house..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "You can still manage to keep readers' attention as long as you tell things from a clever enough angle, even if it's the same old topics."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "For example, reporting on how a scammer once deceived vulnerable girls into relationships, or how a financial criminal was once so poor that they ate a single piece of bread for five days..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That... would definitely get my attention."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But that's not really the kind of news you're after."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "*sigh* You're right, seems you know me pretty well. What I'm really after is exclusive, sensational news pieces that could shake the country. These smaller stories are a waste of my talents."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Oh, I just remembered... I've been following a case lately... well, a series of cases, actually..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "You mean the \"serial disappearances of young women\" case?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "That's right. These stories are the talk of the town right now, and it's probably the most mysterious case we've ever seen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "If I'm the first with a draft ready to publish when the case is finally cracked, and it's the headline story in The Steambird..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "When that happens, I bet all the other reporters will shed tears of envy. I've already gathered all kinds of materials, I just can't wait for the truth to be revealed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So what is the \"serial disappearances of young women\" case? You mean the culprit hasn't been found?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "That's right. The first missing girl case happened almost twenty years ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "And ever since, after a period of time, another girl disappears. What the cases have in common is that the girls are all of a similar age, and that they've all vanished without a trace."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "But the scariest part is that to this day, none of the girls have ever been found."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Many suspects have been arrested over the years in connection with this case. But shortly after each arrest, another disappearance would always happen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Then there must be more than one criminal at work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Maybe there are copycat criminals?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Yes, it's possible. But either way, I believe that every case has some precise truth behind it, waiting to be exposed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Yes, I agree. And at the very least, the families of those missing girls deserve some sort of explanation."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "I just imagined for a second what I would do if Lynette were to suddenly disappear... I'd pay any price to get her back and then find a way to track down the culprit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "Please don't imagine that, Lyney."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
