    "400501": {
        "Desc": "Go to where Lyney is",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "This is our current abode."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Ah, Freminet, you're home. Where did everyone else go? I have some new friends that I would like to introduce."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "Oh, they all just went out a moment ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "I see. Everyone is getting busier now that \"Father\" will be returning soon. I suppose that can't be helped..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Allow me to introduce you to my little brother, Freminet. He is a phenomenal diver."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "Uh, hello..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Nice to meet you! Paimon is Paimon, and this is the {NICKNAME}. You sound very proud to have a diver as a brother, Lyney."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Lyney sure seems to have a big family."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What a talented family."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Haha..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "Uh, Lyney... Could you come here for a moment?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Hmm? What is it, Freminet? Do you have something to tell me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's alright, you go ahead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Hmm... Okay, I see."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is everything alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Oh, it's nothing, we were just discussing a little housework. Sorry for the interruption."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "#Before I forget, {NICKNAME} and I collected more materials to make Magic Pockets. Were you able to get any, Freminet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "Yes, I went diving and gathered lots of materials. I was about to give them to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "That's our Freminet, always quick with the underwater work. Alright, I'll take these to the workshop."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "Looks like... rain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, you're right. But wasn't it clear and sunny just a moment ago? Hmm... Fontaine's weather sure is weird."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Hehe, I'm afraid that's just how it is here. It often rains on days when there are trials being held in the opera house, but don't worry, it'll clear up soon enough."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm? What's wrong, Freminet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "There's a legend about the rain that I tend to believe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "It's said that a Dragon of Water once resided in Fontaine. Though we don't know where the dragon went, every time it weeps, the skies will cloud up and pour out rain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "When I was a child, my mother told me that if I wanted to go outside and play, I should yell toward the sky at the top of my lungs..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "\"Hydro Dragon, Hydro Dragon, don't cry!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Could that Hydro Dragon be the elemental dragon of Fontaine?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Another one of the elemental dragons of Teyvat..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If it's an elemental dragon, then having the power to make it rain wouldn't be very unusual."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let Paimon try something..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Hydro Dragon, Hydro Dragon, don't cry!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Heh... doesn't seem to be of any use. It is just a legend, after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lynette",
                    "T": "You know, you might be a more popular magician if you understood the concept of \"romanticism\"... or could at least play along."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Sorry! It might be because we've never met the Hydro Dragon. Perhaps it can't be comforted by the words of strangers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "After some time, the rain stops."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "It rained for longer than I suspected... Uh, it's already getting late."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Was there something you needed to do, Lyney?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "Yeah, some preparations for the show at the opera house. I need to find a way to catch the last aquabus of the day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "On the day of the performance, just ride the aquabus to the island of Erinnyes. I'll have Lynette meet you at the fountain in front of the opera house."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sounds good. You go ahead, Lyney."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "See you at the performance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "Oh, uh... Are you leaving now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "What is it, Freminet? I'm in a hurry. Oh, I get it. You feel nervous delivering the materials for the Magic Pockets, is that it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "#Perhaps we could trouble {NICKNAME} to help us take these materials to the Beaumont Workshop and deliver them to the owner there?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lyney",
                    "T": "I'm afraid that Freminet can be quite introverted... And the boss there tends to be pretty talkative. Freminet has always been a little afraid of her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No trouble at all. Don't worry, we're on the case!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Freminet",
                    "T": "Sorry for the inconvenience. I'm quite useless when it comes to such tasks... I'll think of a way to make it up to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, no need, no need! This'll be a walk in the park for us."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
