    "400602": {
        "Desc": "Look for clues inside the opera house",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So this is the rope that broke and caused the water tank to fall."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The rope looks pretty durable! How could it be burned through so quickly by fireworks?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(So either Lyney didn't realize this was a safety concern...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Or...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Hmm? Why are you suddenly so serious, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm just looking at where the rope snapped."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa! Look, this bit's made from different material!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Most of it was burned away, but there's still a little bit of it left."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It seems to be flammable."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Like a type of flash cotton."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, so if a rope meant to hold something was made with that kind of material in it, then that means..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, Paimon should write all this down! Let's take notes!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
